In Major League Baseball, current MLB chief operating officer Rob Manfred is elected as the 10th Commissioner of Baseball. He will succeed the retiring Bud Selig in January 2015. (ESPN)The 2016 class of the NASCAR Hall of Fame is announced, consisting of champion drivers Bobby Isaac, Terry Labonte, and Jerry Cook; driver and builder of Charlotte Motor Speedway, Curtis Turner; and the head of Speedway Motorsports, Inc., Bruton Smith. (ESPN)